      	 	<div class="widget" id="dnf_class_values_procurement_notice__description__widget">
			<div class="notice_desc_dates">
				<span class="added">Added: <input type="hidden" name="dnf_class_values[procurement_notice][description][0][added_on]" value="2014-02-05 17:06:31">Feb 05, 2014 5:06 pm</span>
					</div>
		<p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', 'serif'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">The Department of the Air Force, 763d Specialized Contracting Squadron (763 SCONS/PKC) intends to issue a sole source&nbsp; contract&nbsp;to Exelis Inc. The award is to provide MPN-25 and PAR-2000 Radar Support.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>Period of Performance includes a 1 year base period and 2 twelve month option periods.&nbsp;<br /><br />The place of performance for this requirement will be at the contractor's facility as well as deployed system locations, both CONUS AND OCONUS, as specified by the government).<br /><br />The government plans to solicit and make an award for this requirement to only one source under the authority of FAR 6.302-1 and 41 USC 253(c)(1). This is not a request for competitive proposals. Solicitation packages are not available. The approved J&amp;A will be posted at a later date.</span></p>

		<div class="notice_desc_dates">
